videos.headline: Rivers throws INT in the end zone
videos.description: North Texas' Kemon Hall jumps the pass from Bryce Rivers and comes up with a big interception in the end zone for a touchback.

videos.headline: Fine connects with Smith for TD
videos.description: Mason Fine connects at the last second with Kelvin Smith who backs into the end zone for the North Texas touchdown.

videos.headline: Brady powers in for TD from 1-yard line
videos.description: Brenden Brady breaks through the North Texas defense to score a touchdown for UT San Antonio.

videos.headline: Fine throws INT in the end zone
videos.description: Mason Fine's pass is picked off in the end zone by UT San Antonio's Cassius Grady and returned 12 yards.
